-- slice 12: args () returns argv[1..] as a List String.  In the gate the oracle
-- runs with program_args=[] and the native binary runs as ./bin (no extra args),
-- so both sides return [].  Only the empty case is byte-gated; the mdk_cons path
-- is exercised by real argv but not verifiable here (gate limitation noted in
-- PLAN.md slice 12).
main = match args ()
  [] => 0
  _ => 1
